In this exercies you will parse a web site for some particular information and then post that information onto another web page on a different server.

You should create a Python script to do the following:

You need to update your intranet web page with the information about todays lunch at the Utbildning Nord lunch restaurant in Övertorneå.

The information is available some where on www.utbnord.se

The info about todays lunch must be available at your own intranet servers first page, if it's Monday then only Mondays menu should be shown, or on Tuesday then only Tuesdays menu and so on.

The exercise is done when you can show that the script run once per day, automatically finds the correct menu for several days in row.

